{"tid":1083023,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[痴漢列車] 小妹尋日去做義工 俾痴線佬滋擾","createTime":"2019-03-29T10:29:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-30T13:39:37.000Z","uid":112303,"like":4,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"66a096f55d85985393f4af780b853babb717053c","tid":1083023,"uid":112303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T10:29:17.000Z","msg":"小妹就係環保人士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁尋日就去左做一個環保組織搞嘅義工活動，咁就汁下啲垃圾去回收咁啦 （不過唔重要嘅）<br />\n<br />\n重要嘅係同場有一個暗倉金鐘毒撚，戇下戇下，著住件迷你龍tee，仲一路烏低身汁垃圾 好勤力<br />\n<br />\n佢咁辛苦，我咪主動過去幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，點知條毒撚起勢r吹<br />\n<br />\n佢無啦啦話乜我地惺惺相惜 佢都係環保撚黎，即係個啲走塑撚，會自己帶餐具個啲， 我心諗 環保都有好多其他實質方法 洗唔洗咁on9<br />\n<br />\n佢一味大大聲講自己好環保咁，個個都望住我地， 都唔知點應佢，搞到我紅都面曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我feel到佢好撚毒<br />\n<br />\n完左活動佢就問我坐唔坐佢車，我諗住借勢撚走佢<br />\n我:坐車好唔環保㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我：傻豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我個架單車黎<br />\n<br />\n傻乜撚豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我未反應到 佢就笑淫淫咁捉我上車<br />\n<br />\n全程俾佢背脊向後埃係咁抽水<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁去到佢屋企樓下啦，去到大堂佢就拖住我去後樓梯<br />\n<br />\n我:吓 做乜嘢<br />\n佢：搭lift好唔環保<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我不嬲行樓梯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n跟住我轉身走咗<br />\n<br />\n事後佢唔知係邊拎咗我電話<br />\n係咁wtsapp我 我都hea覆佢<br />\n點知佢越黎越痴線 嗌我bb <br />\n又問幾時上佢屋企曳曳 又話乜環保唔用套<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />嚇到我即刻block咗佢"},{"pid":"c29573a56e2cb2b2515e82823ccac6fc0720360a","tid":1083023,"uid":112303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T10:31:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa58c1f4ccba60581d8da5e15c532553e0dca400","tid":1083023,"uid":237848,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T10:32:16.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"e47e66e7a043a8e378d02d2304123120df332c93","tid":1083023,"uid":112303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aa58c1f4ccba60581d8da5e15c532553e0dca400","tid":1083023,"uid":237848,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T10:32:16.000Z","msg":"1/10"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T10:40:34.000Z","msg":"真人真事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4681cb753bc76796d79391f94da720a52f37ec7f","tid":1083023,"uid":154562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T10:43:57.000Z","msg":"［自食其果］尋日去做義工 識左條女 即晚中出左<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1082558\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1082558</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n請相認<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68d6314c1c69f3c9f94389b178d54c3f381212ef","tid":1083023,"uid":112303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4681cb753bc76796d79391f94da720a52f37ec7f","tid":1083023,"uid":154562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T10:43:57.000Z","msg":"［自食其果］尋日去做義工 識左條女 即晚中出左<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1082558\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1082558</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n請相認<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T11:38:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />條友痴線"},{"pid":"e5b7